"By tapping the button, you agree to Service Terms. The device activation information with one-time device location will be sent to HMD Global. Data charges may apply. Data will be used according to Privacy Policy.

Auto Software Update notification will be enabled which installs the latest updates for you. This may use up a small portion of your data budget. The services will access the Internet whenever they need.

These services will cost you overage charges when they access cellular networks.

The device may send device activation information to local operators.

To provide complete service, Google Play Services need to connect to network, access your contact, location, phone, SMS, Microphone, Camera, Sensor, Calendar and storage."

"By tapping the button, you agree to Service Terms. Your data will be processed according to HMD’s Privacy Policy. The device activation information with one-time device location will be sent to HMD Global. Mobile data charges may apply. "
